    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250500/extras/a2aceab7839e013748b4833764af030c.avif?t=1771613947\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250500/extras_big/a2aceab7839e013748b4833764af030c.webp?t=1771613947 width=1560 height=199 /></span><strong></strong><br><br> <br> <br><strong>Rhythia</strong> is a game in which you aim and hit musical beats with precision. You will be targeting blocks, mastering timing, building combos, perfecting your accuracy and climbing leaderboards. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the beginning you will find yourself learning the 3x3 grid layout, aiming at individual blocks and building basic combos by hand, but in short time you can become a rhythm master, with flawless accuracy, perfect timing and seamless aim transitions, all for those satisfying perfect scores. This intense focus on precision and timing rewards dedicated practice, so you will need to develop your aim and musical reflexes to achieve mastery.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250500/extras/2b07fe6dabbe6a06b7db8af05cb334a7.avif?t=1771613947\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2250500/extras_big/2b07fe6dabbe6a06b7db8af05cb334a7.webp?t=1771613947 width=1560 height=443 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Rhythia</strong> offers players unlimited customization of the game - to the smallest detail of gameplay, game interface and elements. It comes bundled with existing shapes, models and presets for you to choose from, and build your own experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
